        "**Example** $\\,$ Suppose the system $\\mathbf{Ax}=\\mathbf{b}~$ is consistent and $~\\mathbf{A}$ is a $5\\times 8~$ matrix and $~\\mathrm{rank}\\,\\mathbf{A}=3.$ $~$How many parameters does the solution of the system have?\n",
