        "\n",
        "$~$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Example** $\\,$ If $\\mathbf{A}$ is nonsingular, then $\\left( \\mathbf{A}^T\\right)^{-1}=\\left( \\mathbf{A}^{-1}\\right)^T$, $~$verify this for\n",
