        "\n",
        "$~$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Example** $\\,$ Consider the system\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "  \\begin{aligned}\n",
        "    x_1 + x_2 &= 1 \\\\ \n",
        "    x_1 +\\epsilon x_2 &= 2 \n",
