        "\n",
        "* To accomplish the last criterion, $~$ we need only select the integer entries of $\\mathbf{A}$ in such a manner that \n",
        "  $\\mathrm{det}\\,\\mathbf{A}=\\pm 1$. $~$ We choose\n",
        "      \n",
